Boinx iStopMotion Home 2.0.2
Animate your story, frame by frame.


Experience the Magic of Creativity

Remember how you watched, fascinated, when King Kong climb the Empire State building? When Luke Skywalker rode the ice beasts? When Wallace and Gromit hunted down the Were-Rabbit? For centuries now, stop motion animation has made the fantasies of film makers come true.

Now it&amp;#039;s time to tell your story, frame by frame.


iStopMotion Home

Want to spend a magic weekend with your kids? Try iStopMotion Home like David Pogue, New York Times technology columnist and editor of the famous Missing Manuals. See why scores of teachers think that stop motion animation is excellent for learning story-telling skills. Feel the enthusiasm, energy and fun that make your kids learn like never before.

